Former Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc.
Managing Director Bradley H. Jack is in plea negotiations with
Connecticut prosecutors regarding a drug-prescription forgery
charge, his lawyer said following a court hearing in Norwalk.  To contact the reporter on this story:
